            {
              "message": "`verified_at` is earlier than the last completed work this document claims to verify. `verification.md` marks T012 complete with commit `df48608`, whose commit time is `2026-04-12T05:11:39Z`, and `metadata.json` was updated at `2026-04-12T05:11:57Z`, but `verified_at` is `2026-04-12T05:00:00Z`. That makes the final verification record chronologically impossible for T012/T013 and breaks consumers that rely on `verified_at` as the actual completion time.",
